      "content": "i know there are people to call but they dont get it. they just keep telling me to \"hang in there\" or \"stay positive\" like that's going to stop my nerves from feeling like they're on fire 24/7. it's not a mental thing, it's my actual body. i'm just so exhausted from fighting a battle that's already lost.",
